<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Arkaan Hilmi Suharsoyo — Portfolio</title>
  
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  
  <!-- External CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css"/>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LANDING -->
      --accent: #2563eb; --accent-light: #3b82f6;
      --gold: #c9a84c; --gold-light: #e8c97a;
      --white: #ffffff; --off-white: #f8f9fc;
      --gray-light: #e8ecf4; --gray: #94a3b8; --gray-dark: #475569;
      --text: #1e293b; --text-light: #64748b;
      --shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(13,27,62,0.10);
      --shadow-lg: 0 20px 48px rgba(13,27,62,0.14);
      --radius: 12px; --radius-lg: 20px;
      --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--off-white); line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }
    ::selection { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--off-white); }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--navy-light); border-radius: 3px; }

    /* LANDING */
    #landing {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 900;
      background: var(--navy);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }
    #landing.hidden { opacity: 0; transform: scale(1.06) translateY(-30px); pointer-events: none; }
    .l-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .l-bg::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -40%; left: -20%;
      width: 80%; height: 80%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(37,99,235,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatB 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .l-bg::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -30%; right: -10%;
      width: 60%; height: 60%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatB 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
    }
    @keyframes floatB { 0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)}50%{transform:translate(2%,3%)} }
    .l-grid {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px),
                        linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
    }
    .l-box {
      position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center;
      max-width: 660px; padding: 2rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
    .l-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(37,99,235,0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.3);
      color: var(--accent-light); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: .35rem 1rem; border-radius: 99px; letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .l-dot { width:6px;height:6px;background:var(--accent-light);border-radius:50%; }
    .l-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:900; color:white; line-height:1.12; margin-bottom:.5rem; }
    .l-title span { color:var(--gold); }
    .l-sub { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size:.95rem; margin-bottom:2.5rem; }
    .l-divider { width:48px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);margin:0 auto 2.5rem;border-radius:2px; }
    .l-q { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size:.95rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .role-row { display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:2rem; }
    .role-card {
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius:var(--radius); padding:1rem 1.4rem; cursor:pointer;
      transition:var(--transition); min-width:130px;
    }
    .role-card:hover,.role-card.sel {
      background:rgba(37,99,235,0.2); border-color:var(--accent-light);
      transform:translateY(-3px);
    }
    .role-card.sel { border-color:var(--gold); background:rgba(201,168,76,0.12); }
    .role-icon { font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:.4rem; }
    .role-lbl { color:white; font-size:.86rem; font-weight:500; }
    .name-wrap {
      display:flex; gap:.75rem; max-width:380px; margin:0 auto 2rem;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius:var(--radius); padding:.5rem .5rem .5rem 1rem; transition:var(--transition);
    }
    .name-wrap:focus-within { border-color:var(--accent-light); background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1); }
    .name-wrap input { flex:1;background:transparent;border:none;outline:none;color:white;font-size:.95rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; }
    .name-wrap input::placeholder { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
    .opt-lbl { font-size:.74rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.33); margin-bottom:.4rem; }
    .btn-enter {
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;
      background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);
      font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;
      padding:.8rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);
    }
    .btn-enter:hover { background:var(--gold-light);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(201,168,76,.35); }
    .btn-enter svg { transition:transform .3s ease; }
    .btn-enter:hover svg { transform:translateX(4px); }

    /* NAVBAR */
    #navbar {
      position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:998;
      background:rgba(13,27,62,0.96);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding:0 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
      height:64px;
    }
    .n-logo { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:white;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px; }
    .n-dot { width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);animation:pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:.6;transform:scale(1.3)} }
    .n-links { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.2rem;list-style:none; }
    .n-links a { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:.83rem;font-weight:500;padding:.38rem .75rem;border-radius:6px;transition:var(--transition);white-space:nowrap; }
    .n-links a:hover,.n-links a.active { color:white;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .n-cta { background:var(--gold)!important;color:var(--navy)!important;font-weight:700!important;padding:.38rem .9rem!important;border-radius:6px; }
    .n-cta:hover { background:var(--gold-light)!important; }
    .n-ham { display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;cursor:pointer;padding:4px; }
    .n-ham span { display:block;width:24px;height:2px;background:white;border-radius:2px; }

    /* MAIN */
    #main-content { padding-top:64px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .6s ease .3s; }
    #main-content.vis { opacity:1; }

    /* HERO */
    #home {
      min-height:100vh;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy) 0%,var(--navy-mid) 50%,#1e3a6e 100%);
      display:flex;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .h-blob1 { position:absolute;top:-100px;right:-100px;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(37,99,235,.15) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%; }
    .h-blob2 { position:absolute;bottom:-150px;left:-80px;width:500px;height:500px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(201,168,76,.08) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%; }
    .h-cont {
      max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 2rem;
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;
      position:relative;z-index:1;width:100%;
    }
    .h-text { animation:fadeL .9s ease; }
    @keyframes fadeL { from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)} }
    .h-badge {
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
      background:rgba(201,168,76,.15);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.3);
      color:var(--gold-light);font-size:.8rem;padding:.3rem .9rem;border-radius:99px;
      font-weight:500;margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;
    }
    .h-name { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.1rem);font-weight:900;color:white;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:.25rem; }
    .h-name span { color:var(--gold); }
    .h-role { font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--accent-light);margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
    .h-desc { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:.98rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.75rem;max-width:460px; }
    .h-tags { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem; }
    .h-tag { background:rgba(37,99,235,.18);border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.3);color:var(--accent-light);font-size:.78rem;padding:.22rem .7rem;border-radius:99px;font-weight:500; }
    .h-contacts { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.65rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem; }
    .c-chip { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);font-size:.82rem;padding:.38rem .85rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;transition:var(--transition); }
    .c-chip:hover { background:rgba(255,255,255,.16);color:white;transform:translateY(-2px); }
    .h-ctas { display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .btn-p { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;background:var(--accent);color:white;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;padding:.72rem 1.5rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition); }
    .btn-p:hover { background:var(--accent-light);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(37,99,235,.4); }
    .btn-o { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;padding:.72rem 1.5rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition); }
    .btn-o:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);color:white;transform:translateY(-2px); }

    /* HERO CARD */
    .h-card {
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;
      animation:fadeR .9s ease .2s both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeR { from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(30px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)} }
    .p-avatar {
      width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--navy-light));
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:700;color:white;
      margin:0 auto 1.2rem;border:3px solid rgba(201,168,76,.5);
    }
    .c-name { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:white;text-align:center;margin-bottom:.2rem; }
    .c-sub { color:var(--gray);font-size:.8rem;text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.4rem; }
    .s-list { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.72rem; }
    .s-item { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.28rem; }
    .s-label { display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.8rem; }
    .s-name { color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);font-weight:500; }
    .s-pct { color:var(--gold-light);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:.76rem; }
    .s-bar { height:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden; }
    .s-fill { height:100%;border-radius:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--gold));width:0;transition:width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1); }
    .h-stats { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:.7rem;margin-top:1.4rem; }
    .stat-b { text-align:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:10px;padding:.7rem .4rem; }
    .stat-n { font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold); }
    .stat-l { font-size:.7rem;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px; }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section { padding:5rem 2rem; }
    .s-white { background:var(--white); }
    .s-light { background:var(--off-white); }
    .s-navy { background:var(--navy); }
    .container { max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto; }
    .sec-hdr { text-align:center;margin-bottom:3.5rem; }
    .sec-tag { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(37,99,235,.1);border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.2);color:var(--accent);font-size:.77rem;font-weight:600;padding:.28rem .88rem;border-radius:99px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.88rem; }
    .sec-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:.7rem; }
    .sec-title-w { color:white; }
    .sec-desc { color:var(--text-light);font-size:.97rem;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto; }
    .sec-div { width:48px;height:3px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:2px;margin:.7rem auto 0; }

    /* EDUCATION */
    .edu-card {
      background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);
      border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.25rem;
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:78px 1fr;gap:1.75rem;
      margin-bottom:1.5rem;transition:var(--transition);position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .edu-card::before { content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:4px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--accent),var(--gold));border-radius:4px 0 0 4px; }
    .edu-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);transform:translateY(-3px); }
    .edu-logo { width:68px;height:68px;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--navy-mid));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.6rem;color:white;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; }
    .edu-period { font-size:.79rem;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:.35rem; }
    .edu-school { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.18rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.2rem; }
    .edu-major { color:var(--text-light);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.7rem; }
    .edu-meta { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.45rem;margin-bottom:.9rem; }
    .e-badge { background:rgba(37,99,235,.08);border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.15);color:var(--accent);font-size:.76rem;font-weight:600;padding:.18rem .65rem;border-radius:6px; }
    .e-badge.gld { background:rgba(201,168,76,.1);border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.25);color:#a07830; }
    .edu-res h4 { font-size:.86rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.45rem; }
    .edu-res ul { padding-left:1.15rem;color:var(--text-light);font-size:.86rem;line-height:1.82; }
    .edu-docs { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.45rem;margin-top:.85rem; }
    .doc-chip { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:var(--gray-light);border:1px solid #d8e0ef;border-radius:6px;padding:.28rem .65rem;font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text-light);cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition); }
    .doc-chip:hover { background:var(--navy);color:white; }

    /* EXPERIENCE */
    .exp-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.4rem; }
    .exp-card { background:white;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:1.7rem;transition:var(--transition);position:relative; }
    .exp-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow);transform:translateY(-4px); }
    .exp-type { position:absolute;top:1.2rem;right:1.2rem;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.18rem .58rem;border-radius:99px; }
    .t-org { background:rgba(201,168,76,.12);color:#a07830; }
    .t-work { background:rgba(37,99,235,.1);color:var(--accent); }
    .exp-icon { width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:.85rem; }
    .i-org { background:rgba(201,168,76,.12); }
    .i-work { background:rgba(37,99,235,.1); }
    .exp-period { font-size:.77rem;color:var(--text-light);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:.3rem; }
    .exp-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.02rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.18rem; }
    .exp-org { font-size:.83rem;color:var(--accent);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:.7rem; }
    .exp-desc { font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.68; }

    /* PROJECTS */
    .proj-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.4rem; }
    .proj-card { background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;transition:var(--transition);display:flex;flex-direction:column; }
    .proj-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);transform:translateY(-5px); }
    .proj-thumb { height:130px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--navy-light));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:2.6rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden; }
    .proj-thumb::after { content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 50%,rgba(0,0,0,.25) 100%); }
    .proj-body { padding:1.2rem;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column; }
    .proj-tags { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.38rem;margin-bottom:.65rem; }
    .proj-tag { font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.13rem .5rem;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(37,99,235,.08);color:var(--accent); }
    .proj-name { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:.98rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.38rem; }
    .proj-desc { font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.64;flex:1; }
    .proj-foot { margin-top:.9rem;padding-top:.7rem;border-top:1px solid var(--gray-light);display:flex;gap:.5rem; }
    .proj-link { font-size:.76rem;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px; }
    .proj-link:hover { text-decoration:underline; }

    /* TRAINING */
    .train-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1.2rem; }
    .train-card { background:white;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.4rem;display:flex;gap:.9rem;align-items:flex-start;transition:var(--transition); }
    .train-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow);transform:translateY(-3px); }
    .train-icon { width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--navy-mid));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.15rem;flex-shrink:0; }
    .train-yr { font-size:.74rem;color:var(--accent);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.18rem; }
    .train-name { font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.18rem; }
    .train-org { font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-light); }

    /* SKILLS */
    .sk-wrap { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start; }
    .sk-cat { margin-bottom:1.8rem; }
    .sk-cat-title { font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:.9rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px; }
    .sk-cat-title::after { content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--gray-light); }
    .sk-tags { display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.48rem; }
    .sk-tag { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:8px;padding:.42rem .82rem;font-size:.81rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);transition:var(--transition); }
    .sk-tag:hover { background:var(--navy);color:white;border-color:var(--navy); }
    .int-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:.9rem; }
    .int-card { background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.2rem;text-align:center;transition:var(--transition); }
    .int-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow);border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-3px); }
    .int-icon { font-size:1.9rem;margin-bottom:.55rem; }
    .int-name { font-size:.86rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.22rem; }
    .int-desc { font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.48; }

    /* GALLERY */
    .gal-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem; }
    .gal-item { border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;background:var(--navy-mid);aspect-ratio:4/3;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:2.4rem;position:relative;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition); }
    .gal-item::before { content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--navy-light));opacity:.85; }
    .gal-item:hover { transform:scale(1.04);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); }
    .gal-icon { position:relative;z-index:1; }
    .gal-lbl { position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:.65rem;background:linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(0,0,0,.6) 0%,transparent 100%);color:white;font-size:.76rem;font-weight:500;z-index:2;opacity:0;transition:var(--transition); }
    .gal-item:hover .gal-lbl { opacity:1; }

    /* MESSAGE */
    .msg-wrap { max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;background:var(--off-white);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem; }
    .f-group { margin-bottom:1.2rem; }
    .f-lbl { font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.48rem;display:block; }
    .f-inp,.f-ta,.f-sel { width:100%;padding:.72rem 1rem;background:white;border:1.5px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:8px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text);outline:none;transition:var(--transition); }
    .f-inp:focus,.f-ta:focus,.f-sel:focus { border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,.1); }
    .f-ta { resize:vertical;min-height:115px; }
    .f-row { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem; }
    .btn-send { width:100%;background:var(--navy);color:white;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;padding:.85rem;border-radius:8px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:.5rem; }
    .btn-send:hover { background:var(--navy-light);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(13,27,62,.3); }
    .ok-msg { display:none;background:rgba(34,197,94,.1);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;text-align:center;color:#16a34a;font-weight:500;font-size:.88rem;margin-top:1rem; }

    /* FREELANCE */
    #freelance { position:relative;overflow:hidden; }
    .fl-bg { position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:50px 50px; }
    .fl-hdr { text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;position:relative;z-index:1; }
    .fl-badge { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.15);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.3);color:var(--gold-light);font-size:.77rem;font-weight:600;padding:.28rem .88rem;border-radius:99px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.88rem; }
    .avail-dot { width:7px;height:7px;background:#4ade80;border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s infinite; }
    .fl-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;position:relative;z-index:1; }
    .fl-card { background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:1.5rem 1.2rem;text-align:center;transition:var(--transition);cursor:pointer; }
    .fl-card:hover { background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-5px); }
    .fl-emoji { font-size:2.1rem;margin-bottom:.7rem; }
    .fl-name { color:white;font-size:.86rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.38rem; }
    .fl-desc { color:rgba(255,255,255,.42);font-size:.74rem;line-height:1.48; }
    .fl-cta { text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;position:relative;z-index:1; }

    /* PPT */
    #ppt-sec { background:var(--off-white);padding:3rem 2rem;text-align:center; }
    .ppt-wrap { max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;background:white;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem; }
    .ppt-icon { font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:.9rem; }
    .ppt-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:.45rem; }
    .ppt-desc { color:var(--text-light);font-size:.87rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1.6; }
    .btn-ppt { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c0392b,#e74c3c);color:white;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:.94rem;font-weight:600;padding:.85rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:var(--transition); }
    .btn-ppt:hover { transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(192,57,43,.4); }
    #ppt-prog { display:none;margin-top:1rem; }
    .prog-bar { height:4px;background:var(--gray-light);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:.45rem; }
    .prog-fill { height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--gold));border-radius:2px;width:0;transition:width .4s ease; }
    #ppt-status { font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:.38rem; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background:var(--navy);color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);text-align:center;padding:2rem;font-size:.8rem; }
    footer strong { color:rgba(255,255,255,.8); }
    footer a { color:var(--gold-light);text-decoration:none; }

    /* REVEAL */
    .reveal { opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease; }
    .reveal.vis { opacity:1;transform:translateY(0); }
    .d1{transition-delay:.1s}.d2{transition-delay:.2s}.d3{transition-delay:.3s}.d4{transition-delay:.4s}

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media(max-width:900px){
      .h-cont{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .h-card{display:none}
      .exp-grid,.proj-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .fl-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
      .gal-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
      .sk-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .int-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
      .train-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .f-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .edu-card{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    }
    @media(max-width:640px){
      .n-links{display:none}
      .n-ham{display:flex}
      .n-links.open{display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:fixed;top:64px;left:0;right:0;background:var(--navy);padding:1rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);z-index:997}
      .role-row{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
      .fl-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LANDING -->
<div id="landing">
  <div class="l-bg"><div class="l-grid"></div></div>
  <div class="l-box">
    <div class="l-badge"><span class="l-dot"></span>Selamat Datang</div>
    <h1 class="l-title">Halo! Sebelum masuk,<br/><span>siapakah Anda?</span></h1>
    <p class="l-sub">Pilih role Anda agar kami bisa menyapa dengan tepat</p>
    <div class="l-divider"></div>
    <p class="l-q">Saya mengunjungi portfolio ini sebagai…</p>
    <div class="role-row">
      <div class="role-card" onclick="pickRole('HRD Perusahaan',this)"><div class="role-icon">💼</div><div class="role-lbl">HRD Perusahaan</div></div>
      <div class="role-card" onclick="pickRole('Mahasiswa',this)"><div class="role-icon">🎓</div><div class="role-lbl">Mahasiswa</div></div>
      <div class="role-card" onclick="pickRole('Kolega / Rekan',this)"><div class="role-icon">🤝</div><div class="role-lbl">Kolega / Rekan</div></div>
      <div class="role-card" onclick="pickRole('Calon Klien',this)"><div class="role-icon">🌟</div><div class="role-lbl">Calon Klien</div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="opt-lbl">✦ Nama Anda (opsional — tidak wajib diisi)</p>
    <div class="name-wrap">
      <input type="text" id="vname" placeholder="Tulis nama Anda di sini…" maxlength="60"/>
      <button class="btn-enter" onclick="enter()">
        Masuk
        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav id="navbar" style="display:none">
  <a href="#home" class="n-logo"><div class="n-dot"></div>Arkaan H.S.</a>
  <ul class="n-links" id="nlinks">
    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="#education">Pendidikan</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Pengalaman</a></li>
