          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="edu-card reveal d1">
        <div class="edu-logo" style="font-size:1rem">SMA</div>
        <div>
          <div class="edu-period">2019 — 2022</div>
          <div class="edu-school">SMA / Sekolah Menengah Atas</div>
          <div class="edu-major">IPA · [Nama Sekolah — isi sesuai data Arkaan]</div>
          <div class="edu-meta">
